3. The Bigger Unlock: Simulation

Right now most systems are:

observe → react

This becomes:

simulate → choose → act

You can ask:
	•	“What happens if we add a transit line here?”
	•	“What happens if 3 competitors enter this zone?”
	•	“What happens if income rises but mobility drops?”

That’s a sandbox for reality decisions.

